snippet: One moment, Wayne Rooney madly celebrated the triumph of ending years of criticism for his World Cup struggles. Then, the England striker left the field with his head down in disappointment....

headline.print_headline: Rooney's First Career World Cup Goal Not Enough
headline.main: Rooney's First Career World Cup Goal Not Enough

lead_paragraph: One moment, Wayne Rooney madly celebrated the triumph of ending years of criticism for his World Cup struggles. Then, the England striker left the field with his head down in disappointment.
